GLM-5.2 QuantTrio DCP2-327K recipe for 4x NVIDIA DGX Spark (GB10)

The model this recipe serves:

- GLM-5.2 by Z.ai (Zhipu AI) — the model itself, including the in-checkpoint
  MTP draft layer and DSA sparse attention that make this deployment possible.
  https://z.ai / https://huggingface.co/zai-org
- QuantTrio — the unpruned Int4-Int8Mix quantization of GLM-5.2.
  https://huggingface.co/QuantTrio

This repository adapts and builds upon the following Apache-2.0 licensed work:

- CosmicRaisins/glm-5.2-gb10 — the GLM-5.2 sm_121 serving stack, the
  DCP2/DCP4 recipes this repo reproduces, the vendored vLLM patches, and the
  index_topk_pattern and clear_thinking findings.
  https://github.com/CosmicRaisins/glm-5.2-gb10
- tonyd2wild/GLM-5.2-QuantTrio-200K-4x-DGX-Spark — the QuantTrio recipe
  lineage, launch harness this repo's launcher derives from, and the indexer
  MTP-overhang fix.
  https://github.com/tonyd2wild/GLM-5.2-QuantTrio-200K-4x-DGX-Spark
- local-inference-lab/vllm (branch codex/dcp-globaltopk-sharddraft-defaults-20260622)
  and the vLLM project — the serving engine. Patch files in patches/ and
  upstream-lse-experiment/ contain code derived from vLLM (Apache-2.0,
  Copyright contributors to the vLLM project).
- lukealonso/b12x — the CUDA-graph-safe sparse-MLA kernel library.
- eugr/spark-vllm-docker — the image build harness.

